## 11. Politici recomandate pentru endpoint-uri API

### Timesheets
- `POST /api/projects/:id/timesheets`
- `GET /api/projects/:id/timesheets`
- `PATCH /api/projects/:id/timesheets/:timesheetId`
- `DELETE /api/projects/:id/timesheets/:timesheetId`

### Cost entries
- `POST /api/projects/:id/cost-entries`
- `GET /api/projects/:id/cost-entries`
- `PATCH /api/projects/:id/cost-entries/:costEntryId`
- `DELETE /api/projects/:id/cost-entries/:costEntryId`

### Risks
- `POST /api/projects/:id/risks`
- `GET /api/projects/:id/risks`
- `PATCH /api/projects/:id/risks/:riskId`
- `DELETE /api/projects/:id/risks/:riskId`

Toate aceste endpoint-uri trebuie să aplice:

- autentificare obligatorie,
- validare project-level access,
- validare de ownership unde este cazul,
- validare de integritate între entități.

